We randomly selected a group of potential winners, and we decided to award the person who answered a surprise FaceTime call 🤯
.
We appreciate everyone who has shown support through the years, and we enjoy giving back 💨
.
We’re still in the giving mood, so whoever tags the most people below will win a King Palm Care Pack with flavors, accessories, and clothes 🚨
.
#kingpalmgiveaway #allnaturalproducts🌿
